    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-01-26T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-01-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="31"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d31">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Dayton</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 465.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-01-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 26, 1864.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to my instruction of the 16th instant,
                    No. 461, I have to inform you that, under the date of the 31st ultimo, Mr. Lane,
                    the consul of the United States at Vera Cruz, writes that on that date he had
                    received a verbal communication from Mr. Mansfield, the consul at Tabasco,
                    confirming the report that he is in prison there, and allowed no means of
                    communicating with his friends, and that his sentence is a year’s
                    imprisonment.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William L. Dayton</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
